title: #92Noon! Bercich/Russo/Gellner/LaVelle
description: Nordo is gone, but PA has World Cup fever, talking about Russia's incredible upset over the weekend. Fishing and football talk with Pete Berchich stops in to talk fishing and football. Marney Gellner talks about the heat AND humidity at Wrigley Field for the Cubs-Twins series, and more Twins and heat talk with LaVelle E. Neal III!
